Adspresso wrote a review Feb 2019
Penang Island, Malaysia112 contributions61 helpful votes
Awesome stay for 2 days
Loved the infinity pool. Great for all those amazing Instagram shots. Hotel service was excellent. Staff are always helpful and smiling. Room was spacious and comfortable. Had the food at The Top restaurant by the pool, not bad and you get to enjoy both sea view and city view. Also the night view was amazing at The Top. Many convenient store behind the hotel. Mi Quang restaurant also behind. Just a short walking distance away. Great stay and recommended
