Khanh Linh wrote a review Feb 2019
Hobart, Australia10 contributions
Lovely stay for the whole family
Booked the delight plus 2 bedroom apartment just 24 hours prior the trip due to my previous accommodation cancelling on us. The apartment has great view to the beach from the master bedroom. The opposite building is under construction so view from common area was blocked. Staff were very responsive to our requests/questions. Location is 10/10 with the beach right across the road and several mini marts and restaurants surrounding the hotel. Breakfast buffet was also great. My only complaint is that the second bedroom felt a bit stuffy without any windows. Definitely good value for your money.
