Kris K wrote a review Feb 2019
Torquay, Australia177 contributions22 helpful votes
+1
Spectacular roof top pool.
Really, what more do you want! I loved this roof top area. In a hot climate I always look for an amazing pool with views/atmosphere to die for and this one is a serious contender for best. The views across the ocean and coastline are insane going in both directions. The water was at a welcoming temperature and I spent hours at different times of the day soaking up the ambience. Awesome! The pool was large enough, even when it was at its busiest you could still find a corner to be wowed! At other times like at seven in the morning I had the pool to myself or with only one or two others. The sunrise swim I highly recommend. Worth an early wake. Downsides of the pool area are that it’s hard to find shade and you have to walk through the bar in your bathers to go to the…
Date of stay: July 2018
